creator: Kiwee Games & Apps
descriptionHtml:
Quickly enter the information you want to save for later. Easily switch to the keyboard with one button on the standard keyboard and insert text.

Phraser is a shortcut keyboard app, it saves your email templates, canned support replies, fast form completion, addresses, phone numbers, email addresses, emoji, or anything you type regularly, and just need one tap when inputting.

This app will really help you a lot if you are too lazy to enter the same text manually all the time, such as greeting messages.

Phrase Keyboard has the following features:
- Saving any number of phrases.
- The function of auto sending a message (does not work on all messengers)
- Double text insertion function
- Convenient and stylish keyboard with saved phrases


How to setup Phraser Keyboard
Open Settings app -> General management -> Language and input -> On-screen keyboard -> Manage keyboard, then enable Phraser Keyboard and click OK.

And now you can use Phrases Keyboard in any app.

If you have any questions or wishes, please write to this email kiweeapps@gmail.com
descriptionShort: Save often-used phrases, passwords, emails and answers in Phraser Keyboard
